Class EventQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • EventQueue

  • public class EventQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class maintains a queue of events used for simulating the behaviour of the system. Events are kept in a cronologically sorted list. This class is an example of a priority queue (event time being the priority in this case).
